PrecisAmendments to the INDIAN INCOME TAX REMISSION ORDER which extend to the 1994 taxation year amounts payable to a taxpayer by an employer residing on a reserve or Indian settlement in respect of an office or employment, where the office or employment was held continuously since before 1994.

precis:
Amendments to the INDIAN INCOME TAX REMISSION ORDER which extend to the
1994 taxation year amounts payable to a taxpayer by an employer residing
on a reserve or Indian settlement in respect of an office or employment,
where the office or employment was held continuously since before 1994.
